{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading","text":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.3.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Version"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","ex